data.description: Well-built vintage home in the vibrant Berkley community.  Newly remodeled kitchen, updated bathroom new paint and blinds add to the charm of this 1920 home. Multiple off alley parking and a spacious backyard with storage shed provide opportunity for outside enjoyment.  Perfect for a retirement home as it is within walking distance to Tennyson Street which offers dinning and shopping. Solidly built this home could easily be expanded upon. Great investment opportunity in highly sought after neighborhood. The home is being sold in AS IS condition.
